## Rules

- Each test is independent — no shared mutable state
- Test names describe behavior: `"returns 401 when token is expired"`
- Arrange / Act / Assert structure
- Mock only external I/O (network, filesystem, time) — never mock your own code
- Tests must be deterministic — no random data, no time dependencies without mocking
